{"tid":899134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不甘被男同性戀誘騙性交　男怒殺對方逃6年","createTime":"2018-11-12T07:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T09:48:42.000Z","uid":121473,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0a3a3f5a70cca8251143e0c7fafc65767b2c7a","tid":899134,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAT3KSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAT3KSa.jpg&h=a81fe130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意照。　翻攝《搜狐》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國山東濟南市的舜耕山，6年前發現一具下半身赤裸的男性腐屍，警方後來只查出死者是50多歲的常姓男同性戀，但始終抓不到殺人兇手，直到近日，才在安徽淮南市逮到現年28歲的李姓男疑犯。李男供稱，當年是因為被常男誘姦，他因為不堪受辱才手握石頭把對方砸死。<br />\n<br />\n常男的遺體於2012年10月17日被人發現，他的頭部有多處骨折，下半身裸露，藍色牛仔褲及紅色內褲掛樹枝上。當時遺體已高度腐爛，滿是蛆蟲。警方調查後發現，常男是一名男同性戀，長年在外流浪，喜愛與拾荒者一起吃喝，且有「同性戀行為」。<br />\n<br />\n當年員警方在調閱監視器後，注意到常男死前曾與一名男子進入舜耕山，研判男子涉有重嫌，但因當時拍下的畫面太模糊，無法看清長相，因此案情始終未能突破。<br />\n<br />\n直到日前，警方透過新技術，才確認嫌犯李男的身份，並於上月8日在淮南市謝家集區一間麻雀館內把他拘捕。李男供稱，2012年離職後，因為不願回家而流浪街頭，隨後遇到常男，對方說要帶他一起賺錢，於是才跟著進入舜耕山。沒想到，到了懸崖邊後，常男提出性行為的要求，李男多次拒絕後，仍遭強行脫掉衣服，最後他不甘受辱、情緒失控，便把常男推下山，再手握石頭，多次砸頭讓對方死亡。<br />\n <br />\n李男又說，犯案後他照常過一般生活，直到案發後一周無意間發現警方貼出懸賞通報，才會離開濟南，跑到安徽謝家集區的麻雀館打工。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181112/1464717/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181112%2F1464717%2F&d=qdWU1xkqc807tCKxwTAPS9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fe7680f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181112%2F1464717%2F&h=e6f4e994\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181112/1464717/</a>"},{"pid":"06c2c5f3a1e4c3a39dd470e3a14e8b281e93b079","tid":899134,"uid":75033,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"抵死 死gay佬"},{"pid":"c75a5a85bba6483c3816efd5d8c6b45d4bb34c48","tid":899134,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"25cedca7b8ec3baa99cfa2e7f961f8d85b94fddc","tid":899134,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c51aadfffa69d896c85adb8778c97db983d6525","tid":899134,"uid":21963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25cedca7b8ec3baa99cfa2e7f961f8d85b94fddc","tid":899134,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"襯佢唔為意一野扑落佢個頭到<br />\n佢已經wing wing 地反抗唔到<br />\n跟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非gay"},{"pid":"0d70eff326fd69a1b45e08270de389bda6adc260","tid":899134,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c51aadfffa69d896c85adb8778c97db983d6525","tid":899134,"uid":21963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25cedca7b8ec3baa99cfa2e7f961f8d85b94fddc","tid":899134,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"襯佢唔為意一野扑落佢個頭到<br />\n佢已經wing wing 地反抗唔到<br />\n跟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}